EntityFramework.Functions library works on .NET 4.0, .NET 4.5, .NET 4.6, with Entity Framework 6.1.0 and later.
It can be installed through Nuget: - Install-Package EntityFramework.Functions -DependencyVersion Highest
For more information, see: - Document (APIs and examples): https://weblogs.asp.net/Dixin/EntityFramework.Functions - Source code: https://github.com/Dixin/EntityFramework.Functions - Nuget package: https://www.nuget.org/packages/EntityFramework.Functions
Thanks for the contribution of SteveRuble.
